    "Quote": "I'm glad mushrooms are against the law, because I took them one time, and you know what happened to me? I laid in a field of green grass for four hours going, \"My God! I love everything.\"Yeah, now if that isn't a hazard to our country  how are we gonna justify arms dealing when we realize that we're all one?"
